metadata.name: Iceland Camp Ticket 2022
metadata.description: NFT Iceland Camp will be a multi day long exclusive event from September 22nd-28th of this year. This camp will be a gathering of artists, collectors, creatives, and builders all with the purpose of driving innovation and fun within the NFT community. Attendees can expect a myriad of artwork and outdoor events that highlight the awe of Icelandic nature. It is our goal, as the Metascapes team, to bridge the gap between our beautiful world with the Metaverse.
